9,"quote":{"pid":"885f5324a42127f22d7589ebbe4fae00d2c15ee0","tid":2015631,"uid":103156,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T23:35:37.000Z","msg":"梗爽：未必源自「長征」。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T23:51:12.000Z","msg":"恥爽:「長征的確墮落了，但擊中非洲的物體不一定中國的長征」<br />\n「個別媒體稱擊中非洲的是『中國長征衛星』極不負責任，我們對此堅決反對」，強調調查長征墮落的地點工作仍在進行中，聯合國也多次表示衛星墮落是全球現象，現在應該關注如何避免衛星再墮落、反對汙名化中國衛星技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T02:22:30.000Z","msg":"你個名<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5242c097ebfea8065831b91fd03adb60cfd9e7d","tid":2015631,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3f541f142b1eb3629f8ffe6adb6a6f9603b89f56","tid":2015631,"uid":8011,"like":48,"dislike":179,"score":-131,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T23:08:43.000Z","msg":"用美國芯片，有後門<br />\n用中國芯片，冇技術<br />\n<br />\n完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T02:25:25.000Z","msg":"講到中國芯片冇後門咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54789eed65b11a6ccca88fe39ef9e0370f017965","tid":2015631,"uid":274055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c091b256e1ddc15ad4e1d4a68ae9a66e071d5334","tid":2015631,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T23:03:07.000Z","msg":"落地殘骸曝光！中國「長征五號B」失控擊中非洲國家<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3164723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3164723&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=9ac78433\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3164723&h=b974ab53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3164723</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國最大火箭「長征五號B」5日發射後，成為近30年來最大的失控重返大氣層物體，昨（12）日經美軍追蹤殘骸掉落西非附近的大西洋海域，現有外媒踢爆，來自該火箭的12公尺金屬物體擊中非洲國家象牙海岸（Republic of C&ocirc;te d'Ivoire）。<br />\n<br />\n哈佛天體物理學家麥克道威爾（Jonathan McDowell）在推特表示，1個12公尺長的金屬物體墜入象牙海岸當地村落，該物底掉落的位置，位於長征五號B型火箭的再入軌道上，與火箭重返大氣層的位置距離2100公里，該部位殘骸在掉落過程中可能已被空氣「切片」（磨擦燃燒之意）。<br />\n<br />\n非洲媒體《Aminata 24》報導指出，這個10多公尺的的金屬物體從天而降，目前正在等待政府進行調查，提供民眾更多資訊，以避免非洲人民的生命受到危害。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅今（13日）主持例行記者會，對於《美國有線電視新聞網》（CNN）提問是否能證實「長征五號B」擊中非洲國家？趙立堅僅回應，「我不了解你說的情況，建議你向主管部門詢問」。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T02:31:36.000Z","msg":"呢條殘骸<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EX006jhX0AIBTd7?format=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEX006jhX0AIBTd7%3Fformat%3Djpg&h=bd2732ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f78e9b4f0066db8542ecdd273aa4f3265dc80312","tid":2015631,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a584604745dcdb41e821a64ba96c0e03ebefd27","tid":2015631,"uid":32577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9b20c0d5801eb5e8f5418edfb3161cf77454e27a","tid":2015631,"uid":49359,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"3f541f142b1eb3629f8ffe6adb6a6f9603b89f56","tid":2015631,"uid":8011,"like":48,"dislike":179,"score":-131,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T23:08:43.000Z","msg":"用美國芯片，有後門<br />\n用中國芯片，冇技術<br />\n<br />\n完"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T00:50:26.000Z","msg":"晶片<br />\n同我炒一千次影相post上黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T01:48:13.000Z","msg":"抄<b